 Linux Shell中捕获CTRL+C

#!/bin/bash

trap 'onCtrlC' INT
function onCtrlC () {
echo 'Ctrl+C is captured'
}

while true; do
echo 'I am working!'
sleep 1
done

Linux中shell脚本获取当前工作目录的方法：

~~~
workdir=$(cd $(dirname $0); pwd)
~~~





